{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 4-5 可能性的末路",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "贝维特以黑暗魔力操控着圣域龙。\\n原初碧龙指出五龙之所以无法恢复\\n原初之力正是因圣域龙的影响。\\n为了恢复力量并帮圣域龙从痛苦中解脱，\\n王子一行迎战圣域龙。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "住手吧！贝维特哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "要是让泽诺斯继续为所欲为，\\n可能性会从这个世界消失的！\\n这真的好吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "谁知道……\\n我倒是想问你，\\n要那种东西又能干什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "干、干什么？\\n你在说些什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "成功与失败、胜利与败北。\\n这些说的不都是结果吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "没有人能在开始之前\\n就知道有没有可能性。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "可你们为什么就能如此\\n天真地相信会有可能性呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "明明有可能只是在\\n朝着早已注定的结局前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "所以可能性这种东西有没有都一样。\\n因为最终迎来的结局只有一个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我实在是无法理解\\n你们为什么要执着于这种无用之物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可能性是无用之物！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "没错……也许你们不能理解，\\n但没有可能性其实才是幸福的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "幸福！？没有可能性才会幸福！？\\n贝维特哥哥……\\n你到底在说些什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "算了吧，尤蒂尔。\\n和他对话根本没有意义。\\n只要以力服人就行了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "呵呵……\\n我也喜欢这种简单明了的方法。\\n那我就让你们看一个好东西吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "出来吧，圣域龙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "圣域龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120246_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "啊哈哈哈哈！\\n由你们尊崇已久的圣域龙来杀了你们，\\n是不是感到很光荣？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "圣域龙……\\n被黑色魔力所囚而沦为傀儡吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "当世之风啊……\\n我明白你们为何无法恢复原初之力了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "你感受不到这风吗。\\n火与水、光与暗……你从圣域龙身上\\n感受不到我们的原初之力吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "唔！？\\n从圣域龙身上！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120246_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "的确如此……\\n可为什么圣域龙会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "你们的力量并非有所缺损，\\n只是力量化作了风与火这些元素，\\n循环于世间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "原本只要你们能够明白这一点，\\n恢复力量并不是难事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "然而却有着另外的家伙\\n在你们浑然不觉之时\\n执掌了循环于世间的元素。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "也就是世界的管理者……\\n圣域龙吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "真是太会给人找麻烦了！\\n连别人的力量都抢，\\n这家伙到底要干什么啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "也许是想亲自\\n对抗“起始之人”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "哈！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "也许是想要像曾经的我们那样，\\n汇聚原初之力，\\n让自己成为“起始之龙”的容器——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "又或是打算\\n以自己的意志和力量\\n为消灭“起始之人”做准备。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "可圣域龙不是想要\\n复活“起始之人”吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "对啊。\\n圣域龙不是否定了“起始之龙”\\n所追求的可能性的世界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "即便圣域龙对可能性不抱希望，\\n但也不会容忍“起始之人”掌控世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "圣域龙应该是觉得\\n“起始之人”的掌控并不会给\\n世间的生命带来好的影响。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "所以才想要获得力量，\\n由自己来阻止“起始之人”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "也许是想要由自己去管理\\n那因“起始之人”而失去可能性的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "圣域龙打算全都自己完成！？\\n为什么要做到这种地步……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也许……是因为“爱”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "圣域龙爱着这个世界，\\n也爱着世间所有的生命……\\n无论是龙还是我们人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "人类对圣域龙来说……\\n不，甚至连龙也都是\\n圣域龙所要守护的对象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以圣域龙才没有依靠他人的帮助，\\n或是让他人来承担起这份责任吧。\\n因为圣域龙打算独自背负这一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也难怪。若是原初五龙还在的话也许\\n能够另当别论……但当今之世却已\\n没有能与圣域龙相提并论的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "没有任何人可供依靠的圣域龙……\\n感觉好可怜啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "虽然不记得转生前的事情，\\n但听了这样的话，\\n感觉自己也应该承担些责任呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "圣域龙素来仁慈。\\n我们选择成为“起始之龙”的\\n容器之时也曾表示过反对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "圣域龙会在下次危机来临之时\\n选择自己承担而不用牺牲他人\\n也不足为奇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "所以才会汇聚我们的\\n原初之力变成那个样子吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120246_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "这可真是有趣。\\n也就是说，\\n那就是可能性的末路吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔！\\n你竟然说那是可能性的末路！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "所有人都相信着自己的可能性，\\n做出自己认为妥善的选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "但是结果却只有一个。\\n别说去消灭那个人了，\\n圣域龙自己反倒沦为了棋子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你们则因此无法获得\\n与那个人对抗的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "而造成这种结果的，\\n正是反抗了圣域龙的你们自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "正因为你们追求什么可能性，\\n结果才会失去了一切可能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "真是有趣。\\n这结果不是充分证明了\\n寻求可能性是一件多么愚蠢的事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果一切都在此结束……\\n那你说得或许没错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但现在结局还未见分晓。\\n未来也还留有无限的可能性，\\n并且会不断延续下去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没错。\\n圣域龙也许用错了方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "但那深深的爱却没有错。\\n身为曾经尊崇圣域龙的巫女，\\n我将在这里向你证明这一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你们这对兄妹……\\n真是让人感到烦躁啊。\\n算了，反正结果早已注定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_08_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "去吧，圣域龙！\\n亲手毁灭你所爱的人类吧！",
